What will happen to me?

506
00:59:08,373 --> 00:59:12,122
Hey, you're looking for a fight,
so I'm the one who's scared.

507
00:59:13,538 --> 00:59:17,830
You used to lend an ear whenever
I wanted to talk about Kyoichi.

508
00:59:17,830 --> 00:59:21,331
You did that on purpose.
You knew how I felt about him.

509
00:59:22,497 --> 00:59:26,247
You feigned sympathy but always tried to break us up.

510
00:59:30,414 --> 00:59:31,747
Excuse me!

511
00:59:35,747 --> 00:59:37,164
Welcome.

512
00:59:37,164 --> 00:59:39,914
- Singha, please.
- I'll have a Carlsberg.

513
00:59:39,914 --> 00:59:41,414
Certainly.

514
00:59:43,830 --> 00:59:46,747
- I'll buy. What do you want?
- I'll pay for myself.

515
00:59:46,747 --> 00:59:47,830
Yeah?

516
00:59:53,538 --> 00:59:54,997
Leave him alone.

517
01:00:02,206 --> 01:00:03,914
Here you go.

518
01:00:10,747 --> 01:00:13,830
Excuse me. This and this, please.

519
01:00:15,414 --> 01:00:16,830
Certainly.

520
01:00:20,331 --> 01:00:22,872
It took me a long time to get here.

521
01:00:22,872 --> 01:00:25,081
I'm pretty much at the end of my rope.

522
01:00:25,081 --> 01:00:26,664
How long have you liked him?

523
01:00:26,664 --> 01:00:28,747
Since the day we met.

524
01:00:28,747 --> 01:00:30,580
What's so great about him?

525
01:00:30,580 --> 01:00:32,206
Is there ever a reason?

526
01:00:33,664 --> 01:00:35,331
8 years, huh?

527
01:00:36,247 --> 01:00:39,664
It must have been so hard. You did well.

528
01:00:43,763 --> 01:00:47,013
If you continue, it'll just cause you more pain.

529
01:00:47,937 --> 01:00:49,937
Give it up and free yourself.

530
01:00:54,738 --> 01:01:00,113
Kyoichi is like a rat
that willingly follows the Pied Piper.

531
01:01:01,263 --> 01:01:03,929
I can't let him drown in a gutter.

532
01:01:09,138 --> 01:01:10,263
A gutter?

533
01:01:11,637 --> 01:01:12,679
A gutter.

534
01:01:14,188 --> 01:01:15,604
Welcome.

535
01:01:25,596 --> 01:01:26,929
What are you doing?

536
01:01:28,513 --> 01:01:30,513
Why did you tell her to come see you?

537
01:01:33,263 --> 01:01:38,346
I called him. I figured we'd make
more progress if we were all involved.

538
01:01:46,472 --> 01:01:48,346
Did you tell her anything weird?

539
01:01:52,138 --> 01:01:53,513
Speak up.

540
01:01:55,145 --> 01:01:56,603
What do mean, weird?

541
01:02:03,261 --> 01:02:06,763
Hey, since you're here, decide now.

542
01:02:06,763 --> 01:02:11,472
Me or Imagase? Which will you take home tonight?

543
01:02:11,472 --> 01:02:12,513
Huh?

544
01:02:14,346 --> 01:02:15,679
What, all of a sudden?

545
01:02:19,353 --> 01:02:20,353
Welcome.

546
01:02:21,263 --> 01:02:23,280
Oh, a Carlsberg.

547
01:02:24,846 --> 01:02:25,929
Come on.

548
01:02:31,430 --> 01:02:33,096
Don't tell me you can't decide.

549
01:02:33,888 --> 01:02:35,763
What the hell is this?

550
01:02:38,829 --> 01:02:42,829
Do you understand? I'm a woman and he's a man.

551
01:02:45,378 --> 01:02:46,586
I know that.

552
01:02:51,703 --> 01:02:53,287
Here you go.

553
01:02:59,662 --> 01:03:01,412
How far have you two gone?

554
01:03:02,912 --> 01:03:05,079
Wait, never mind, don't tell me.

555
01:03:11,538 --> 01:03:14,829
You're being swayed by him, Kyoichi.

556
01:03:16,329 --> 01:03:19,162
If you don't bail now, it'll be too late.

557
01:03:19,162 --> 01:03:24,212
You corner him so relentlessly.
How typically feminine.

558
01:03:24,212 --> 01:03:28,462
Men will die if you don't leave a way out.
Especially his type.

559
01:03:31,037 --> 01:03:37,120
You can't forget him because
you gave him your virginity, right?

560
01:03:41,662 --> 01:03:46,496
